title: ArcGIS Server Mode
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: GPL
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors the ArcGIS Server site mode.

 EDITABLE is considered OK. READ_ONLY is a valid maintenance state, but is WARN
 by default because services cannot be started, stopped, or modified while the
 site is read-only. Unknown modes are UNKNOWN by default.
item:
 This check has no item.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when Server mode data is present.
